description: A part of Burlington for the last 70 years, Beansie's Bus is a local institution. Occupying the same spot since 1944, Beansie's continues to serve up the classic burgers, hot dogs, sandwiches, and all the other fine fare that's earned them a place in the hearts and minds of their community. With a history of friendly, welcoming service and quality food, Beansie's Bus is sure to warm your heart and fill your belly time and time again.
name: Beansie's Bus
